# Football Analytics Platform

## Business Problem

Football clubs collect large amounts of data but often struggle to convert data into actionable insights.

## Solution

Build an end-to-end analytics platform using Microsoft Fabric, Power BI and Python.

## Target Users

* Coaches
* Analysts
* Sporting Directors

## Key Questions

* Which teams are overperforming compared to expected goals?
* Which players create the most value?
* How does team form develop over time?
* Which players are potential transfer targets?

## Technologies

* Microsoft Fabric
* Power BI
* GitHub
* Python
* SQL

## Success Criteria

Create a modern cloud-based analytics solution capable of ingesting, transforming and visualizing football data.
